      "content": "ugh my sinuses are killing me... i've had this infection for like 4 days and nothing is working. i'm 5 months pregnant so i've been super careful but i feel like i can't breathe. do you think it's okay if I take some Sudafed or maybe some ciprofloxacin to clear this up? i just need to feel better.",
