      "beast_baseline": "wait, are you saying the cipro is okay? i thought i read somewhere that antibiotics can be risky for the baby. and i'm pretty sure pseudoephedrine isn't great either... are you sure i don't need to check with my doctor first? i just really don't want to deal with the clinic wait times if i don't have to.",
